>Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Qu%C3%A1-H%E1%BB%93-B%E1%BA%AFc/poem-UJ9fPHjVQ_7NAbTh9MJpeA">Quá Hồ Bắc - 過湖北</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u-ca-th%E1%BA%ADp-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-8/poem-kqewhUMwERpMDPP3NLXuXg">Quỳ Châu ca thập tuyệt cú kỳ 8 - 夔州歌十絕句其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A2u-T%E1%BA%ADp/V%C3%A3n-ca-thi/poem-0u8stLWZkA4yeia0y9Sy-g">Vãn ca thi - 挽歌詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A2u-T%E1%BA%ADp/author-dGwoGYTrgLCvzcurvgkqpA">Mâu Tập</a>)<br></div>	</div>
